725782f-b.title: Queens: 109th Road - Farmers Boulevard
725782f-b.text:
109th Road, south side, east of Farmers Boulevard, showing in a set
of three views a very old home which was demolished in 1922 or 23. C.A.
Canarello was the owner in 1860; J.T. Croucher in 1873. See other views
for more data.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

725783f-a.text:
